downloadTitle: Oracle to SQL Server Migration Handbook
downloadDescription: Oracle to SQL Server Migration Handbook

downloadFile.name: Oracle to SQL Server Migration Handbook.pdf

detailsSection:
The purpose of this document is to provide detailed explanation of features/functionalities enabled in the Oracle database, recommended migration approach, and any required workaround. This document can help migration planners and designers to understand the features used in source databases, effort involved in the migration. 
This document was prepared based on the information available at the time, for example, the capabilities of Oracle Database, SQL DB Server, and migration tools such as SSMA.
detailsSection_file_name: Oracle to SQL Server Migration Handbook.pdf
installInstructionSection: To start the download, click Download, click Go, and then do one of the following: To start the installation immediately, click Open or Run this program from its current location. To copy the download to your computer for installation at a later time, click Save or Save this program to disk.
